title: Microsoft Azure Redis Cache - replication
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the replication status across a geo-replicated Microsoft
 Cache for Azure cluster.

 The thresholds can be configured using the rule "Azure Redis replication".

 Note that these metrics are only available when geo-replication is enabled
 which is not available on every tier.

discovery:
 One service is created, provided the metric is provided by Azure.
